metadata.name: Hana Microelectronics Public Company Limited
metadata.description: Hana Microelectronics Public Company Limited, together with its subsidiaries, manufactures and trades in electronic components. It offers printed circuit board assemblies and integrated circuits. The company also provides agent and customer services. It has operations in Thailand, Malaysia, China, Taiwan, the United States, Hong Kong, and internationally. The company was founded in 1978 and is headquartered in Bangkok, Thailand.
